<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="el">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, viewport-fit=cover">
  <title>Офлайн | Politografisi.online</title>
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f172a 0%, #1e293b 100%);
      color: #f8fafc;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      min-height: 100vh;
      padding: 2rem;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .container { max-width: 400px; }
    .icon {
      font-size: 4rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      animation: pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
    }
    @keyframes pulse {
      0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
      50% { opacity: 0.5; }
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
      color: #93c5fd;
    }
    p {
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: #94a3b8;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }
    button {
      background: #1d4ed8;
      color: white;
      border: none;
      padding: 0.75rem 2rem;
      border-radius: 0.75rem;
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background 0.2s;
    }
    button:hover { background: #2563eb; }
    button:active { background: #1e40af; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="icon">📡</div>
    <h1>Εκτός σύνδεσης</h1>
    <p>Δεν υπάρχει σύνδεση στο διαδίκτυο. Ελέγξτε τη σύνδεσή σας και δοκιμάστε ξανά.</p>
    <button onclick="window.location.reload()">Δοκιμάστε ξανά</button>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
